## Features
- add monochrome icon [#62](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/pull/62) ([aliernfrog](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/f3ba8b0f0d26101646e0ecb5556b77c6522b3ed1))
- **maps**: multi-selection [#63](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/pull/63) ([alieRN](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/64a910eb25c7abe4cc03de0735344c70efb1cfb7))
- progress dialog when doing file actions [#64](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/pull/64) ([alieRN](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/c6a64d0c61721ea49bcd7f89d5eae68457ee82c2))
- open .txt files with LAC Tool (#65) [#65](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/pull/65) ([alieRN](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/f8e2edce96cae9740df3e786c3d3a83701914a5d))
- **maps**: ability to duplicate maps [#66](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/pull/66) ([alieRN](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/4bff1365e2619a0d55c2138ddbf6885c45c1ce0b))
- UI improvements [#67](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/pull/67) ([alieRN](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/1c7ccdbce3ef5a92175fe1adabeb7c7f8d6d8738))
- language selection [#68](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/pull/68) ([alieRN](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/748d7646b386218b0219266e2ff126c496110a53))
- **l10n**: add Turkish translations [#69](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/pull/69) ([alieRN](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/8831b390e1f395d8569671b8f3c8e6ea312e32aa))

## Bug Fixes
- make all alert dialogs scrollable [#62](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/pull/62) ([alieRN](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/08eb812445778511005f862bc88003412b6f9153))

## Continuous Integration
- pass GitHub token for packages [#62](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/pull/62) ([alieRN](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/fc8ca3e809576a64406d978681773fd6f87a5295))

## Chores
- update dependencies [#62](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/pull/62) ([aliernfrog](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/f01f307a4e19d7ef8c29e8218876ccec9a70ab2e))
- update top-toast, material and material3 [#62](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/pull/62) ([alieRN](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/af875d604dfbb4645c2d29e68ecdbf3c819a8c55))
- update app version to v3.1.0 (31000) [#62](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/pull/62) ([alieRN](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/4cc9f75454ef708f5af9bc8070b50d8cd369c8ed))
- merge branch `dev` into `main` [#62](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/pull/62) ([alieRN](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/commit/b1eae774026a1e99d47203096644ba391a466311))

View this release on [GitHub](https://github.com/aliernfrog/lac-tool/releases/tag/v3.1.0)
